verbose_text: In addition, the results showed that a 2%-SD, a 4%-SD and an 8%-SD significantly decreased the expression of dFOXO gene (P < 0.01), and exercise training significantly increased the dFOXO gene expression in the 0%-SD flies, 2%-SD flies and 4%-SD flies (P < 0.01, P < 0.01, P < 0.05, respectively), but dFOXO gene expression of the 8%-SD flies did not change significantly after exercise training (P> 0.05) (XREF_FIG B).
